fs/dcache.c: fix kmemcheck splat at take_dentry_name_snapshot()

Since only dentry->d_name.len + 1 bytes out of DNAME_INLINE_LEN bytes
are initialized at __d_alloc(), we can't copy the whole size
unconditionally.

